    {
      "id": "18d4750c-f3ba-8052-a068-d430e8f9b003",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Logs are a good form of detecting Learning Strategies, but not only that, transitions between log behaviors are also helpful. Thus, the authors use a dataset of 41 courses to see how in-course behavior changes affect performance. Authors use Markov Models to examine behavioral shifts (changes in strategy).",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "18d4750c-f3ba-8052-a068-d430e8f9b003",
        "parent": {
