    {
      "id": "18d4750c-f3ba-8097-a01a-d6cd403622a2",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Results show that it is possible to identify clear clusters with measurable impacts on student performance. Surface approaches tend to underperform deep approaches over time. Secondly, more interestingly, being consistent with one approach is better than being irregular. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "18d4750c-f3ba-8097-a01a-d6cd403622a2",
        "parent": {
